== But it should be nice! ==

By~the~way we would like to notice that Luwrain does not want to~be~an~ordinary project.
We have~to~do~everything possible to~make it~interesting and attractive.
In~pursuit of~that aim any~ideas  how~to~improve user impressions,
how~to~make usage easier 
or how~to~eliminate one more boring and time consuming thing 
will be definitely appreciated here.
If once Luwrain users fill themselves  using 
something that is not a~accessibility technology anymore 
we will treat such moment as~a~real success 
making Luwrain itself something very close to a~state of~the~art.

Luwrain is rather specific  in~this sense as~it has such intention 
being not a~commercial product. 
That has corresponding explanation:
commercial companies  always are not free from the~one serious problem:
all products they  originate usually die at~the~moment of their fault
or at~the moment when their products do not yield gain any more.
It is a~really serious problem because in~these circumstances 
a~lot of users can be left without a~tool they really need.

== Research part ==

Another important part of~Luwrain idea is an~acceptance of~results 
given by~modern scientific research in~relevant areas if there are any.
The~world of~information technologies is not frozen.
It~changes permanently  and Luwrain should reflect such changes properly.
So everybody can fill himself completely free to~propose new ideas to~Luwrain for~experimental implementation if that does not violate ten terms stated at~the~top of this page.

